                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">“青灯永夜，时一展卷，恍然类昨日事，而一时朋游沦落，如晨星霜叶，而余亦老矣”，笔墨浮华，类同梦华录，尽是黍离之悲，已而自咏叹，草草毕览，或难同焉。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1160722086">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1160722086" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1160722086" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1160722086">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/133808201/">撄宁</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">宋人太会吃！看着名字就饿……但掩卷那种风流云散的感觉啊……“古今多少事，都付笑谈中”得多豁达才能做到</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1155222888">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1155222888" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1155222888" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1155222888">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/51398038/">Antia</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一部承载南宋临安市井气息的生活笔记，一曲追忆旧时杭州由盛及衰的时代挽歌。其时南宋已亡，家国倾覆，身为故臣遗老，周密拒不降元，抗节隐遁，仿孟元老《东京梦华录》体追思故土，笔耕成书。遥想当年，临安城湖山歌舞，靡丽纷华，繁盛平和，四时悠然。周密以其盛写其衰，深寓黍离之悲。然文笔灿然，摇曳生姿，单就市井民俗的采风记述而言，趣味横生，用木心先生的话来评价就是，“论衣食住行，古代才享受。现代比古代寂寞得多了。”</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1148737218">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1148737218" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1148737218" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1148737218">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/128192868/">三生一锦</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">上天作证，我真的是看着“武林”两个字进来的，孤陋寡闻了，真看起来喜欢周密。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1126360223">
